protein description: Cytochrome b-c1 complex subunit 7; Component of the ubiquinol-cytochrome c reductase complex (complex III or cytochrome b-c1 complex), which is part of the mitochondrial respiratory chain
ATP synthase subunit beta; Produces ATP from ADP in the presence of a proton gradient across the membrane
NADH dehydrogenase (ubiquinone) Fe-S protein 1; Belongs to the complex I 75 kDa subunit family
Solute carrier family 25 alpha, member 5; Belongs to the mitochondrial carrier (TC 2.A.29) family
Ribosomal protein S23; Belongs to the universal ribosomal protein uS12 family
